description: Developed web applications with MERN stack and Vue.js, boosting user engagement by 20%. Engineered RESTful APIs with Express.js and Nest.js, optimizing database operations with Prisma ORM and PostgreSQL for 30% faster performance. Integrated HTML5, React, and Plyr video players to enhance media playback. Conducted comprehensive API testing with Postman, ensuring 100% functionality and scalability.
